Class WorldMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.model.world.WorldMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WorldMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Overworld view of the game world. 2/16 Easy (el-5 to el-8) - plains 10/16 Moderate (el-4) - forest 3/16 Difficult (el-3 to el) - mountains 1/16 Very difficult (el+1) - swamp forest is the background. have 2 plain areas (1 is player start), 3 mountain areas and 1 swamp. TODO would be nice to have tiles reflect the official d20 terrains (add desert and hill)

    alex
